reviewText: A low budget film that is not worth viewing.
Yes! Love these kind of movies.
This achieved the shouting at the TV effect that got me to realise I had lost the plot by believing the peril on the screen. I would recommend this if you are up to it!
After a rash of "el chupacabra" sightings, a hiking tour manager decides to profit by creating a "Goat Sucker" hiking tour. Only, there may be more to the sightings than just legend.
